node-identifier: string
in path

ID of node-identifier

200 OK
pfx-sid_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK) 
{
  
"pfx-sid": {Prefix SID

    
"vflag": "boolean", V Flag

    
"pflag": "boolean", P Flag

    
"sid-prefix": {Prefix

      
"af-name": "string", AFName

      
"ipv4": "string", IPv4 address type

      
"ipv6": "string" IPv6 address type

    },
    
"nflag": "boolean", N Flag

    
"eflag": "boolean", E Flag

    
"sid-type": "string", SID Type

"rflag": "boolean", R Flag

    
"lflag": "boolean" L Flag

  }
}
